metadata.name: Pepe Holmes Golden Pass
metadata.description:
Dear collectors and fans of Pepe Holmes,

We are excited to announce the launch of our Pepe Holmes Golden Pass NFT, the ultimate ticket to exclusive benefits for our most dedicated supporters. With the Golden Pass, you'll receive access to a range of perks, including discounts, allow listing, giveaways, white-listing, and entry passes for exclusive events.

As a small but passionate group of artists, our dream is to create amazing Pepe Holmes art, illustrations, and animations for you to enjoy. However, we need your support to make this dream a reality. Our future plans and projects all depend on the success of our Golden Pass sales.

By minting our Golden Pass NFT, you are not only getting access to a range of exclusive perks and rewards, but you are also supporting our small business and helping us continue to create incredible Pepe Holmes art for years to come.

We hope you will consider supporting us by minting our Golden Pass NFT and becoming a part of our growing community of Pepe Holmes enthusiasts. Thank you for your support!

Sincerely,  
Pepe Holmes.com
